---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import HeroBanner from '../components/HeroBanner.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Less Than Truck Load (LTL)" description="LTL shipping services - efficient and cost-effective less-than-truckload shipping across 48 states.">
  
  <HeroBanner title="Less Than Truck Load (LTL)" backgroundImage="/images/hero-loading.png" />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="content-section__text">
          <h2>LTL Shipping Services</h2>
          <p>The load-to-truck ratio is a critical aspect of the trucking industry and one of the many reasons why we offer an exclusive LTL service. We have maintained an efficient business model that allows us to provide you with a wide selection of your shipping needs.</p>
          <p>Our strategic national LTL centers allow us to optimize routes and reduce costs while maintaining the highest standards of service. We understand that not every shipment requires a full truck, and our LTL services provide a cost-effective solution for smaller loads.</p>
          <p>With our extensive network of carriers and logistics professionals, we can ensure that your LTL shipments are handled with care and delivered on time. Whether you need to ship pallets, crates, or other smaller freight, our LTL services are designed to meet your needs efficiently.</p>
          <a href="/contact-us" class="btn btn--primary" style="margin-top:15px;">Request A Quote</a>
        </div>
        <div class="content-section__image">
          <img src="/images/ltl-loading.png" alt="LTL Loading Bay" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
